Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.31,0:00:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.51,0:00:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，屍體是不會說話的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…誰？
