Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.93,0:02:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}審判者的攻擊\NArbiter attack
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦艦長亞力克斯‧羅威\N派傳令兵前來參見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來報告內容吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告皇帝陛下\N雖然比預定時間晚了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.26,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過貨物已經載上銀之戰艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.33,0:03:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳去轉告艦長\N務必要謹慎處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨她去\N現在是貴賓的散步時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你們把它收拾掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.04,0:06:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還不曉得艦長要打算\N怎麼處理來客呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著，在這裡比起艦長說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.58,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須更優先重視\N魏斯洛隊長的美觀要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是給她看到那堆廢銅爛鐵\N還待在那裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得那位有潔癖症的公主\N會說什麼唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們太缺乏自動自發的精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是誰負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈囉，小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張，別緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經奉命\N要把妳當成貴賓來接待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎，我要放手囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳保持安靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡的回音很大聲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去通知艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨物目前在停機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，我會轉告艦長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒薇絲人在停機庫裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，跑到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是在這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，她喜歡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，露一手每次玩的那招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才藝表演就看我的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以放輕鬆一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.85,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在銀之戰艦上的感覺怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以隨時在艦內自由走動哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶路，跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.89,0:08:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你看，是艾兒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.67,0:09:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，要給妳的東西也在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，這麼說來艾兒\N這是誰給妳的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉很恐怖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是繼續躺著比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對你太粗暴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說那些維修人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好清澈的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這艘船上\N會有這麼清澈的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為銀之戰艦\N是世界上最安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你也來吃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和艦長談談嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，您方便嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有話要說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算對艾兒怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？你想怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答不出來是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是沒辦法保護她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總比把她放在這艘船上安全吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這片天空裡，你想做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛越大風暴區…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.23,0:11:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，有身分不明的飛行物體\N正在接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒備敵人入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍，戒備敵人入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機15…不，共18架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位120，距離兩萬五千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方的全速戰鬥時間\N是二十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要撐過這段時間就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機全速戰鬥時間為二十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機全速戰鬥時間為二十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認貨物目前位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，這聲音是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過可以肯定的是\N我們不能再待在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.59,0:12:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是先鋒艇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要引擎沒壞就可以飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要撐過二十分鐘\N就是我們贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要用先鋒艇迎戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是停機庫\N客人們都在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，艾兒薇絲她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她帶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有夠遜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.74,0:14:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問迪奧殿下您也要出征嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，還不到時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇后吃兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號機中彈，脫離戰線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號機中彈，一樣脫離戰線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對空砲火無法追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右後方三號高射砲嚴重受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓升降機固定在上層飛行甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫脫離戰線的戰機\N從上層甲板登艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.90,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心\N這小子一定飛得起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.77,0:15:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，克勞士\N這裡是你鎖上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就轉不開啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對不起，讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.88,0:15:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡是\N世界上最安全的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你閃一邊去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算它受損再嚴重\N就算它變得再破爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它還是我們的先鋒艇呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.14,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會待在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…待在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才要飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說你幼稚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒薇絲交給我照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維修長，中彈的二號機回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備滅火器和拖車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.23,0:16:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.21,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把升降機升上去\N三號機要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升降機要上去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號機讓開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.05,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特星型機一架侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星型機一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊薩，把升降機固定在上甲板\N別讓它下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是停機庫，有敵機侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有敵機侵入\N基爾特星型機一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機侵入，準備應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第二甲板\N左舷裝甲遭到擊破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機侵入進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功侵入目標內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是拼命哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明都還搞不清楚\N那到底是不是正牌貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.50,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被彈開了！？\N艦長可是一發畢命的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家艦長跟這些傢伙\N不知道交手過幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經驗差很多好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把輔助鏡頭轉到左邊的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下你可回不了大風暴區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇死掉了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.21,0:19:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.05,0:19:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有備用的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八點鐘方向，距離四哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定有一艘在準無音航行狀態\N中的監察型基爾特船艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它似乎在追蹤本艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放過第二波的離艦音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.97,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長說她想讓客人\N用先鋒艇去出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨她高興怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎\N真的要讓他們坐上去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長都已經准許了\N你就不要再囉唆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把彈匣拿過來啦，伊薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.12,0:20:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關槍子彈兩百發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果把扳機按著不放\N二十秒就會射光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要注意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要擔心，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.86,0:20:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我是可以明白啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你想安全回來的話\N請你好好聽我說話好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.91,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,備用彈匣的更換是由後座負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在聽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.49,0:21:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換好彈匣後一定要記得\N用這支操縱桿把子彈裝填好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油結束，升上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在空中距離感很容易出錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要接近到敵機快要\N超出準星範圍的時候再射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保證可以命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要接近戰艦下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.18,0:21:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心會受到克勞地亞磁場影響\N讓先鋒艇在空中解體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要用慣性發動器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.42,0:21:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才已經說過一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你好像太緊張了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點從這兒出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.94,0:21:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太胡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，快換彈匣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.34,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有這條路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.92,0:22:46.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.93,0:22:52.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.23,0:22:57.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.91,0:23:03.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你捨命奮鬥的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.84,0:23:12.48,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.55,0:23:18.42,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.49,0:23:24.33,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.40,0:23:30.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.24,0:23:35.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.98,0:23:46.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.53,0:23:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，我從來沒看過\N有先鋒艇飛得那麼開心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.86,0:23:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來他倒是飛得滿辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.70,0:24:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又從剪式飛行\N換成英麥曼迴轉，厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.54,0:24:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，我們也快上場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.07,0:24:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.48,0:24:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第七話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.11,0:24:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引人入勝的克勞士\NInteresting Claus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.08,0:24:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色那架就交給魯修拉你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.45,0:24:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
